octave.setup        graceplot 1.0.8
platforms           darwin
license             GPL-2+ public-domain
maintainers         nomaintainer
description         Graceplot bindings for octave.  This module does \
                    not work with Octave 3.6 or newer\; this port is \
                    being deprecated.
